text: The Main road 15 is a south–north direction First class main road in the Kisalföld, that connects the Main road 1 change to the border of Slovakia. The road is long.Magyarország, autóatlasz 1:200.000, Honvédelmi Minisztérium Térképészeti Kht., . Most of the traffic was taken over by the M15 motorway. The road, as well as all other main roads in Hungary, is managed and maintained by Magyar Közút, state owned company. ==See also== * Roads in Hungary ==Sources== ==External links== * Hungarian Public Road Non-Profit Ltd.
